{"tid":435133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微波叮大隻硬碟不是夢，40TB硬碟 2019年量產","createTime":"2017-10-14T03:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T13:50:04.000Z","uid":25424,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"752e3af83b53e8f93a92c02916ff569c57470575","tid":435133,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-41611802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-41611802&d=%2BSWCiBjWzNxvCbbo4lMCzQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=551dc469\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-41611802&h=b82f07e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-41611802</a><br />\n原文報導自己睇，大概係講<br />\n<br />\nWD話用一個叫microwave-assisted magnetic recording (MAMR)既技術去寫磁碟，可以將依家3.5吋既硬碟容量加大到40TB<br />\n不過話塊磁碟會燒到成四百度咁高溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成編報導最主要唔係講呢吹水科技，WD話今年會出原型，2018年會交工程樣本俾佢班大客仔試貨，2019年會量產！"},{"pid":"1b1da7db4d5ba75603cc97635aedaffe2ebda730","tid":435133,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613a69efaae7733c674d3637f03fad35894bbef1","tid":435133,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"發布革命性 MAMR 技術！硬碟容量可達 40TB<br />\n| 天師 | 12-10-2017 18:57 | | <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nWD (Western Digital) 最新發布 MAMR (Microwave-Assisted Magnetic Recording) 技術，MAMR 技術可將傳統機械磁性硬碟的容量上限，由現時的 14TB 大幅增加至 40TB，而成本更可與現有 PMR (Perpendicular Magnetic Recording) 技術相近，並較高成本的 HAMR (Heat-Assisted Magnetic Recording) 更理想。<br />\n<br />\n成本與 PMR 相近<br />\n<br />\nWD 宣布的 MAMR (Microwave-Assisted Magnetic Recording) 即微波輔助磁記錄技術，其技術核心利用 Spin Torque Oscillator 產生微波，在提高超高密度下，保持數據存儲的可靠性及穩定性。簡單地說，MAMR 技術就是利用微波取代HAMR 技術內的激光，來作為輔助媒介，好處是可以承襲現有的 PMR 垂直記錄存儲技術及 HelioSeal 充氦封裝，複雜性和成本都較 HAMR 低得多。相對之下，HAMR 技術需要激光波束、玻璃碟片、鐵鉑塗層等新材料，復雜性及成本相當高。<br />\n<br />\n【精選消息】AEON 周年購物盛典！$50 買 Panasonic 運動耳機<br />\n<br />\n【精選消息】【施政報告】港鐵全線列車裝 Free Wi-Fi？搞好 4G 接收先講啦！<br />\n<br />\n【精選消息】【施政報告】資助鄉村鋪光纖！市區唐樓等重建？<br />\n<br />\nWD 透露將在 2019 年出貨第一款 MAMR 技術硬碟，但未有說明容量，但保證能在未來提供超過 4Tb 每平方英寸的存儲密度 (現時只為 1.xTb)，並可在 2025 年提供 40TB 容量硬碟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=%2BSWCiBjWzNxvCbbo4lMCzQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fe1ba638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>、Western Digital<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDIY 硬碟 WD<br />\n<br />\n相關文章<br />\n12TB 空降腦場！ 巨獸硬碟市況速報<br />\n<br />\n8TB 跌破 HK$2,000！ 巨獸硬碟持續插水<br />\n<br />\n磁帶 60 年不死 IBM、SONY 合作研發 330TB 容量<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp <br />\nFacebook <br />\nLine"},{"pid":"f78ee2d5fbf1d26852b42cd3067ae606c5b0d849","tid":435133,"uid":34010,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"用HDD 烤肉不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b247b460f168e557eb624d037b339e5f36d0db","tid":435133,"uid":49004,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"FHD av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652afad8481a609cac97718810c0669b32541312","tid":435133,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:31:40.000Z","msg":"即刻拎隻4tb入去叮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e8d1529b0fc2eb851ef9ded5dec4f9572e5238","tid":435133,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"d乜柒技術講左十九幾年，宜家最大都係得果十幾tb，仲要貴到仆街<im